data.description: Check an Australian Company Number is valid
data.PS: The following links are only valid for module list maintainers:
data.rationale:
Business::AU::ACN calculates the check number to see if it is a
    valid Australian Company Number. It is also used for Australian
    Registered Scheme Numbers and Australian Registered Body Numbers.

    Note that it does not calculate an Australian Business Number, but
    Business::AU::ABN does that.
